  "Create a new daily note on DAY.

This will create diary/20211129.org on the day 2021-11-29, then
fill it in with the \"daily\" template."
  (interactive)
  (let* ((day (or day (minaduki::today)))
         (now (pcase-let ((`(,y ,m ,d)
